                    <strong>Reviewing Employees Information:</strong>
                    <ul>
                      <li>The table displays details about current employees.</li>
                    </ul>
                  </li>

                  <li>
                    <strong>Performing Actions:</strong>
                    <ul>
                      <li>In the "Actions" column, use the pen icon to edit or the bin icon to delete the corresponding employee information.</li>
                    </ul>
                  </li>

